imdb.plot outline: CEREAL TIME is a web series dedicated to the delicious breakfast cereal we all know and love. In each episode talks about and discusses a specific cereal -- from old classics to brand new cereals that are just hitting shelves. The first and last stop for all of your cereal knowledge, Cereal Time is an extensive look into the numerous breakfast cereals that have been released throughout the years.
imdb.title: Cereal Time
plot: CEREAL TIME is a web series dedicated to the delicious breakfast cereal we all know and love. In each episode talks about and discusses a specific cereal -- from old classics to brand new cereals that are just hitting shelves. The first and last stop for all of your cereal knowledge, _Cereal Time_ (qv) is an extensive look into the numerous breakfast cereals that have been released throughout the years.::Gabriel Fonseca
